1
00:00:06,110 --> 00:00:07,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is this?</font>

2
00:00:08,250 --> 00:00:11,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are these animals?</font>

3
00:00:11,160 --> 00:00:12,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, you have awoken.</font>

4
00:00:13,470 --> 00:00:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As far as I can tell,
you seem to be unharmed.</font>

5
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened to that vampire?</font>

6
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:19,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell happened?</font>

7
00:00:19,470 --> 00:00:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems as though he has disappeared.</font>

8
00:00:22,350 --> 00:00:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evidently, we have been brought
to the outskirts of this town.</font>

9
00:00:26,520 --> 00:00:28,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is their purpose?</font>

10
00:00:30,570 --> 00:00:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't see Watcher.</font>

11
00:00:34,320 --> 00:00:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're awake.</font>

12
00:00:36,730 --> 00:00:40,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were just talking about
whether or not to carry you onto a bed.</font>

13
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe my daughter found you both...</font>

14
00:00:43,440 --> 00:00:45,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">collapsed in the garden.</font>

15
00:00:46,210 --> 00:00:47,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are...</font>

16
00:00:49,250 --> 00:00:52,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Tsubaki Kuruoka!</font>

17
00:02:23,350 --> 00:02:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, go ahead and speak up, Richard.</font>

18
00:02:26,790 --> 00:02:31,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Why did you sneak out of the castle
without permission so late at night?</font>

19
00:02:31,550 --> 00:02:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Mother...</font>

20
00:02:33,130 --> 00:02:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am afraid.</font>

21
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

22
00:02:36,010 --> 00:02:37,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saber?</font>

23
00:02:37,610 --> 00:02:39,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is his past?</font>

24
00:02:39,980 --> 00:02:41,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Afraid? Of what?</font>

25
00:02:42,410 --> 00:02:45,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That I am able to become
proficient at everything.</font>

26
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can do anything well.</font>

27
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:51,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is not a man who can win
against me in swordsmanship.</font>

28
00:02:51,150 --> 00:02:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had thought they were 
all going easy on me,</font>

29
00:02:53,650 --> 00:02:57,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I snuck out of the castle and attacked
bandits infamous for their violence!</font>

30
00:02:57,950 --> 00:02:59,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh my.</font>

31
00:02:59,370 --> 00:03:02,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, I easily trounced them.</font>

32
00:03:03,140 --> 00:03:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what skill I take up,
I master it immediately.</font>

33
00:03:07,810 --> 00:03:12,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People soon become unable
to win against me in contests.</font>

34
00:03:12,350 --> 00:03:15,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At this rate, I will not be able
to make a single friend.</font>

35
00:03:15,420 --> 00:03:21,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it better if I go easy on them and
pretend as if I am not adept at anything?</font>

36
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, he has no charm.</font>

37
00:03:24,570 --> 00:03:27,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said you wouldn't laugh, Mother!</font>

38
00:03:27,830 --> 00:03:32,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Richard, you are indeed a genius.</font>

39
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:33,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However...</font>

40
00:03:33,070 --> 00:03:37,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">being a genius alone will 
not make you a hero.</font>

41
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A hero, you say?</font>

42
00:03:39,210 --> 00:03:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just how King Arthur and the
Knights of the Round Table were as such,</font>

43
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">people only become heroes
after staying firm to their own path.</font>

44
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, if you truly are 
able to do everything...</font>

45
00:03:53,230 --> 00:03:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">cherish the ability to pass on stories.</font>

46
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pass on...</font>

47
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:01,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, I shall tell you...</font>

48
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the story of the King of Knights who raced</font>

49
00:04:04,390 --> 00:04:06,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">through Britain with
a sacred sword in hand!</font>

50
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:09,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But before that...</font>

51
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a mother, I must reprimand you...</font>

52
00:04:12,230 --> 00:04:15,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for leaving the castle without permission.</font>

53
00:04:19,170 --> 00:04:20,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ayaka?</font>

54
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:22,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

55
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Adult...</font>

56
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:25,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha...</font>

57
00:04:26,550 --> 00:04:28,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow!</font>

58
00:04:28,010 --> 00:04:29,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Are you all right?</font>

59
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:33,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you, Saber? Are you okay?</font>

60
00:04:33,470 --> 00:04:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

61
00:04:34,630 --> 00:04:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not perfect, but I can move around.</font>

62
00:04:36,810 --> 00:04:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Healing Magecraft by our allies—</font>

63
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:40,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The reason you left me at the Church...</font>

64
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:44,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was because they could protect me
when you died, wasn't it?</font>

65
00:04:44,690 --> 00:04:45,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

66
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}My apologies.</font>

67
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:49,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you have time to worry about me,</font>

68
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:51,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then you can take
better care of yourself, Saber!</font>

69
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:54,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, that thing earlier...
You should have been able to dodge it.</font>

70
00:04:57,250 --> 00:04:59,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ceiling has been repaired.</font>

71
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:01,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this your Magecraft, too, Saber?</font>

72
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I could do such a thing,</font>

73
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would have fixed
that opera house long ago.</font>

74
00:05:05,990 --> 00:05:07,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are things I can't do, you know.</font>

75
00:05:09,930 --> 00:05:13,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Mother, I am able to become
proficient at everything."</font>

76
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or you said.</font>

77
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You saw that?</font>

78
00:05:18,020 --> 00:05:19,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your mom was really pretty.</font>

79
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:24,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Are you okay?</font>

80
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear that a Master can have dreams
about a Servant's past!</font>

81
00:05:28,690 --> 00:05:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saber, do you still think 
you can do anything?</font>

82
00:05:32,490 --> 00:05:35,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, you actually don't
look like you're terrible</font>

83
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:37,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">at anything other than reading the room.</font>

84
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's going a bit too far!</font>

85
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:43,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There were things I was 
not able to do in life!</font>

86
00:05:43,030 --> 00:05:44,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like what?</font>

87
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:45,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">English.</font>

88
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:47,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

89
00:05:47,030 --> 00:05:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was terrible at English!</font>

90
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:51,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I was the King of England!</font>

91
00:05:55,290 --> 00:05:56,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ayaka!</font>

92
00:05:56,790 --> 00:05:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Laughing about what people 
are not good at—</font>

93
00:05:58,750 --> 00:05:59,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saber...</font>

94
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

95
00:06:01,690 --> 00:06:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you're still alive.</font>

96
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! Switching gears!</font>

97
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:15,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that you know my past embarrassment,
there is nothing left to lose!</font>

98
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:18,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can even win against 
that golden one next time!</font>

99
00:06:18,190 --> 00:06:21,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And no matter what you tell me,
I will protect you, as well!</font>

100
00:06:21,070 --> 00:06:24,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I am a man who can
become proficient at everything!</font>

101
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saber...</font>

102
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Ayaka Sajyou?</font>

103
00:06:33,350 --> 00:06:35,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You all are...</font>

104
00:06:36,930 --> 00:06:38,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, John...</font>

105
00:06:38,290 --> 00:06:40,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There really is nothing 
wrong with your body?</font>

106
00:06:40,980 --> 00:06:43,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that thing earlier... That power...</font>

107
00:06:44,190 --> 00:06:46,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I had a peculiar dream.</font>

108
00:06:46,300 --> 00:06:47,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}A dream?</font>

109
00:06:47,230 --> 00:06:48,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

110
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't really understand it myself...</font>

111
00:06:50,620 --> 00:06:52,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but one thing is for certain.</font>

112
00:06:52,570 --> 00:06:56,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The author Caster gave me some strength.</font>

113
00:06:59,500 --> 00:07:01,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is...</font>

114
00:07:01,150 --> 00:07:05,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The signs of combat are completely gone
from this part of town.</font>

115
00:07:06,590 --> 00:07:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We are likely quarantined within a realm
similar to a Reality Marble.</font>

116
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Reality Marble"?</font>

117
00:07:13,540 --> 00:07:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We would like to suggest
a temporary joining of forces...</font>

118
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in order to escape.</font>

119
00:07:21,850 --> 00:07:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To think they'd set their daughter up
to become a Master...</font>

120
00:07:25,170 --> 00:07:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Tsubaki Kuruoka's Servant
caused this incident?</font>

121
00:07:29,860 --> 00:07:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Correct.</font>

122
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus...</font>

123
00:07:32,470 --> 00:07:34,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there was the mysterious Magecraft</font>

124
00:07:34,180 --> 00:07:36,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that made everyone
on the scene disappear at once.</font>

125
00:07:36,740 --> 00:07:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some of the Servants managed to escape,
but most of them were swallowed whole.</font>

126
00:07:42,170 --> 00:07:47,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}On top of it, a Servant powerful enough
to annihilate the King of Heroes showed up.</font>

127
00:07:56,550 --> 00:07:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you come to defeat the king?</font>

128
00:07:59,970 --> 00:08:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did not.</font>

129
00:08:01,380 --> 00:08:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then...</font>

130
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are you here to pass judgment on me?</font>

131
00:08:05,020 --> 00:08:09,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, who has tarnished the dignity
of your close friend, the king.</font>

132
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:11,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not it, either.</font>

133
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:14,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know about me?</font>

134
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:16,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The king said you were a friend.</font>

135
00:08:17,490 --> 00:08:21,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can only think of
one hero who my king calls</font>

136
00:08:21,350 --> 00:08:23,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"a friend" and compares
his strength against.</font>

137
00:08:24,620 --> 00:08:28,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're thinking I've come
to save King Gilgamesh,</font>

138
00:08:28,610 --> 00:08:30,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm unable to meet those expectations.</font>

139
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you are the king's friend—</font>

140
00:08:33,530 --> 00:08:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because I am his friend.</font>

141
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:39,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gil and I spent irreplaceable 
days together.</font>

142
00:08:39,190 --> 00:08:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An eternal farewell
and the sadness that comes with it...</font>

143
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:45,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are already done and over with.</font>

144
00:08:45,010 --> 00:08:50,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I were the one laying there,
Gil would not be shedding tears.</font>

145
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nor would I want such a thing.</font>

146
00:08:52,780 --> 00:08:55,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can revile me
as much as you want...</font>

147
00:08:55,850 --> 00:08:57,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if that will provide
peace of mind.</font>

148
00:08:57,650 --> 00:08:58,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not it.</font>

149
00:08:59,580 --> 00:09:01,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

150
00:09:01,060 --> 00:09:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do not have a grudge against you.</font>

151
00:09:03,250 --> 00:09:05,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't do anything!</font>

152
00:09:06,370 --> 00:09:08,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You used two Command Spells.</font>

153
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:11,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One to bring him back.</font>

154
00:09:11,530 --> 00:09:13,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One to attempt treatment.</font>

155
00:09:13,780 --> 00:09:16,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is a good decision as a Master.</font>

156
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The reason I came was because I wanted
to know a bit more about the two of you.</font>

157
00:09:22,810 --> 00:09:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About us?</font>

158
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:30,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gil made no attempt to kill the one who
was trying to use him, so I got curious.</font>

159
00:09:30,220 --> 00:09:34,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I thought I'd be able to lend a hand
to a Master like that.</font>

160
00:09:35,070 --> 00:09:37,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In order to get rid of that fiendish god.</font>

161
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's not bad for a temporary shrine.</font>

162
00:09:41,980 --> 00:09:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ishtar, the goddess of Venus...</font>

163
00:09:45,250 --> 00:09:49,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought beings with full Divinity
could not be summoned in a Holy Grail War.</font>

164
00:09:49,820 --> 00:09:52,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, you're right.
Ordinarily, you can't with a Holy Grail.</font>

165
00:09:53,420 --> 00:09:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I manifested because the powers
I had left behind were activated.</font>

166
00:09:58,660 --> 00:10:00,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you do such a thing?</font>

167
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:04,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I burned a blessing onto the world.</font>

168
00:10:05,220 --> 00:10:10,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that disrespectful king and cheeky doll
were to meet once again...</font>

169
00:10:10,590 --> 00:10:13,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will use all of my 
divine body and soul...</font>

170
00:10:13,590 --> 00:10:16,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to protect humans!</font>

171
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn!</font>

172
00:10:19,610 --> 00:10:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell is he doing?</font>

173
00:10:22,070 --> 00:10:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about contacting Miss Tohsaka?</font>

174
00:10:24,770 --> 00:10:26,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady...</font>

175
00:10:26,270 --> 00:10:29,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">do you think Miss Tohsaka
will resolve this problem?</font>

176
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:33,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can bet that very devil
will amplify the problem!</font>

177
00:10:34,570 --> 00:10:36,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That idiot...</font>

178
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it turns out that he
dozed off for all of this,</font>

179
00:10:38,810 --> 00:10:40,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he will never hear the end of it!</font>

180
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

181
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you find something out?</font>

182
00:10:45,970 --> 00:10:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roulettes are lighter than I thought!</font>

183
00:10:49,350 --> 00:10:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

184
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't think that far.</font>

185
00:10:53,470 --> 00:10:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, how was it?</font>

186
00:10:55,550 --> 00:10:58,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems there is electricity.</font>

187
00:10:59,030 --> 00:11:00,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about your end?</font>

188
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:03,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We couldn't find any core for creating
a bounded field in the surrounding area.</font>

189
00:11:04,150 --> 00:11:06,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps it is hidden in 
a very clever manner.</font>

190
00:11:06,940 --> 00:11:11,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once we can find that, there might be
something we can do about this.</font>

191
00:11:12,210 --> 00:11:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm planning on heading 
up to the top floor.</font>

192
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:17,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think the core is there?</font>

193
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:21,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, well, I'd be lucky 
if it was up there.</font>

194
00:11:22,090 --> 00:11:25,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I was hoping to find a place
that's not so well-guarded.</font>

195
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:33,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mister, Miss, I'm glad you got all better!</font>

196
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have our thanks.</font>

197
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. You helped us out.</font>

198
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that thing?</font>

199
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Mr. Black!</font>

200
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:45,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr.... Black?</font>

201
00:11:45,100 --> 00:11:45,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep!</font>

202
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's my friend!</font>

203
00:11:50,660 --> 00:11:52,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come over here.</font>

204
00:11:52,230 --> 00:11:55,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Is that really a Heroic Spirit?</font>

205
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:58,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Is it possible it's a demonic creature
or some kind of phantom?</font>

206
00:11:58,030 --> 00:12:02,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}No. I can't feel any conscience
from that being,</font>

207
00:12:02,010 --> 00:12:03,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}let alone ill will or hatred.</font>

208
00:12:05,140 --> 00:12:07,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those parents are Mages.</font>

209
00:12:07,660 --> 00:12:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if under mental domination,
we might get some information if we talk.</font>

210
00:12:12,340 --> 00:12:13,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He got away!</font>

211
00:12:13,790 --> 00:12:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

212
00:12:15,170 --> 00:12:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

213
00:12:17,060 --> 00:12:18,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's nothing.</font>

214
00:12:19,110 --> 00:12:21,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No clues, huh?</font>

215
00:12:21,010 --> 00:12:22,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We can't even find their corpses.</i></font>

216
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:26,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A majority of the Clan Calatin's
whereabouts are unknown!</i></font>

217
00:12:27,370 --> 00:12:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The King of Heroes disappeared,
but you look depressed.</font>

218
00:12:32,870 --> 00:12:34,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll contact you later.</font>

219
00:12:35,250 --> 00:12:37,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What are you doing here?</font>

220
00:12:37,210 --> 00:12:40,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I was helping out a bit
until a few minutes ago.</font>

221
00:12:40,590 --> 00:12:42,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I hadn't taken a step back to observe,</font>

222
00:12:42,800 --> 00:12:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would've been in that black fog
right about now.</font>

223
00:12:45,410 --> 00:12:46,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha...</font>

224
00:12:46,660 --> 00:12:49,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't remember ever giving such orders!</font>

225
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I don't remember 
receiving them, either.</font>

226
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you, the Servant,
were to be taken down,</font>

227
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that signals the end
of our faction, remember?</font>

228
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:59,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have so many other options...</font>

229
00:12:59,260 --> 00:13:02,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">like recreating a pact
with an unemployed Heroic Spirit.</font>

230
00:13:02,270 --> 00:13:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Are you going to fudge your answer
on that assumption?</font>

231
00:13:05,680 --> 00:13:12,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}If you're the one that set your foot in,
don't be so rash to say that it's over.</font>

232
00:13:12,540 --> 00:13:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You're right.</font>

233
00:13:13,980 --> 00:13:15,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My apologies.</font>

234
00:13:16,330 --> 00:13:18,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like that part about you, ya know!</font>

235
00:13:19,250 --> 00:13:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The cop squad guys are still all right.</font>

236
00:13:22,050 --> 00:13:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you know?</font>

237
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just means there was a Noble Phantasm
that I didn't inform my brother about.</font>

238
00:13:28,010 --> 00:13:29,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, how about it, Brother?</font>

239
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:33,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go help out if it's 
somewhere I can infiltrate.</font>

240
00:13:33,620 --> 00:13:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't give orders 
for you to go that far.</font>

241
00:13:36,380 --> 00:13:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}No, you did!</font>

242
00:13:38,680 --> 00:13:43,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You requested me
to create weapons for your cop squad.</font>

243
00:13:43,220 --> 00:13:46,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That means providing 
power in order to fight.</font>

244
00:13:46,350 --> 00:13:50,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What power can I give 
you guys as an author?</font>

245
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:52,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right! A story!</font>

246
00:13:54,160 --> 00:13:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does that have to do
with you risking danger?</font>

247
00:13:57,520 --> 00:13:59,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">John Wingard.</font>

248
00:14:00,130 --> 00:14:01,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vera Levitt.</font>

249
00:14:01,990 --> 00:14:03,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Annie Cuarón.</font>

250
00:14:03,630 --> 00:14:05,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don Hawkins.</font>

251
00:14:05,410 --> 00:14:07,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chadwick Lee.</font>

252
00:14:07,030 --> 00:14:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuki Capote.</font>

253
00:14:08,380 --> 00:14:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Adelina Eisenstein.</font>

254
00:14:10,830 --> 00:14:12,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their names...</font>

255
00:14:12,290 --> 00:14:13,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not just names, you see?</font>

256
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:16,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Faces, voices, origins...</font>

257
00:14:16,300 --> 00:14:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything I found out,
they're all in here in their entirety.</font>

258
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You learn all the names
of your subordinates, don't you?</font>

259
00:14:23,010 --> 00:14:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're all central 
characters in my piece now.</font>

260
00:14:27,010 --> 00:14:30,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And they're acting out
the most supreme of scenarios.</font>

261
00:14:30,470 --> 00:14:31,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that's the case...</font>

262
00:14:31,350 --> 00:14:34,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you just wanna have front 
row seats to watch...</font>

263
00:14:34,060 --> 00:14:35,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}don't ya?</font>

264
00:14:36,870 --> 00:14:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We believe that in order to escape from
this world, we must defeat the Mage...</font>

265
00:14:42,110 --> 00:14:44,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who is at the root of all this.</font>

266
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:45,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Vera...</font>

267
00:14:45,950 --> 00:14:47,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was it?</font>

268
00:14:47,690 --> 00:14:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do we really have to 
defeat them to get out?</font>

269
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe there's a way to 
secretly and safely escape.</font>

270
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:56,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe that's difficult.</font>

271
00:14:56,460 --> 00:14:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you are a Mage yourself,
I think you would understand.</font>

272
00:14:59,460 --> 00:15:02,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh no, I'm not anything like that.</font>

273
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:06,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words, someone is executing
this great a level of Magecraft!</font>

274
00:15:06,980 --> 00:15:10,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is such an amazing bounded field!
The Servants surely are—</font>

275
00:15:10,350 --> 00:15:12,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you really a Servant?</font>

276
00:15:12,970 --> 00:15:15,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem to be pretty relaxed.</font>

277
00:15:15,890 --> 00:15:16,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are?</font>

278
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:19,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm John Wingard.</font>

279
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">John...</font>

280
00:15:20,540 --> 00:15:22,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see, John!</font>

281
00:15:22,540 --> 00:15:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a chance encounter of sorts!
Let's get along, shall we?</font>

282
00:15:26,130 --> 00:15:28,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you guys were talking about</font>

283
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">eradicating the Mage or Servant
that started all this, right?</font>

284
00:15:32,470 --> 00:15:36,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are many of my allies who would be
relatively averse to doing so.</font>

285
00:15:36,750 --> 00:15:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Myself included.</font>

286
00:15:38,430 --> 00:15:41,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The girl you tried to protect...</font>

287
00:15:42,060 --> 00:15:43,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsubaki, was it?</font>

288
00:15:43,930 --> 00:15:45,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's still the possibility...</font>

289
00:15:45,980 --> 00:15:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that the one who locked us in
was that girl's Servant, right?</font>

290
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:52,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that little girl is 
the root of all evil...</font>

291
00:15:52,970 --> 00:15:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will you guys be able to kill her?</font>

292
00:15:58,370 --> 00:15:59,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Black...</font>

293
00:16:00,330 --> 00:16:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember when we first met?</font>

294
00:16:04,670 --> 00:16:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sorry! I'm sorry!</i></font>

295
00:16:07,950 --> 00:16:11,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Father, Mother, I'm sorry!</i></font>

296
00:16:12,260 --> 00:16:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will do a proper job!</i></font>

297
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will endure it better!</i></font>

298
00:16:17,890 --> 00:16:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So...</i></font>

299
00:16:20,060 --> 00:16:22,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>please, don't abandon me!</i></font>

300
00:16:30,430 --> 00:16:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an6}I ASK YOU</font>

301
00:16:30,430 --> 00:16:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I ask you.</i></font>

302
00:16:32,570 --> 00:16:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are you...</i></font>

303
00:16:34,310 --> 00:16:35,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>my...</i></font>

304
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:37,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an6}ARE YOU
MY MASTER?</font>

305
00:16:35,680 --> 00:16:37,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Master?</i></font>

306
00:16:37,990 --> 00:16:39,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>Who is it?</i></font>

307
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I am...</i></font>

308
00:16:41,520 --> 00:16:43,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tsubaki Kuruoka.</i></font>

309
00:16:43,870 --> 00:16:46,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be together forever, right?</font>

310
00:16:49,090 --> 00:16:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Black?</font>

311
00:16:51,380 --> 00:16:55,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not saying it's the right 
answer to kill a girl...</font>

312
00:16:55,470 --> 00:16:57,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">nor do I want to kill.</font>

313
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

314
00:16:58,790 --> 00:17:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we might end up in a situation
where someone has to do it, right?</font>

315
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:06,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have braced myself for that possibility.</font>

316
00:17:06,770 --> 00:17:08,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

317
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We...</font>

318
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:13,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When the time comes, I'll do it.</font>

319
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:17,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end...</font>

320
00:17:17,220 --> 00:17:20,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't be the knight that I adored.</font>

321
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:22,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you guys are different!</font>

322
00:17:23,330 --> 00:17:24,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are skilled knights!</font>

323
00:17:25,250 --> 00:17:29,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Against that fearful bowman,
you fought and survived!</font>

324
00:17:29,690 --> 00:17:31,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All in order to save a single young girl!</font>

325
00:17:32,300 --> 00:17:37,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you lot must be the kind
that will protect the innocent!</font>

326
00:17:38,050 --> 00:17:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides...</font>

327
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:41,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}after doing <i>that</i> once...</font>

328
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:43,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}pulling the trigger becomes easier.</font>

329
00:17:43,840 --> 00:17:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I should be the one 
shouldering that burden.</font>

330
00:17:46,630 --> 00:17:48,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saber...</font>

331
00:17:50,650 --> 00:17:53,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like the base for some faction.</font>

332
00:17:53,630 --> 00:17:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This room really feels like 
it's the least guarded.</font>

333
00:17:58,690 --> 00:18:00,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right here.</font>

334
00:18:00,770 --> 00:18:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The location closest to 
outside the bounded field.</font>

335
00:18:03,830 --> 00:18:06,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only see it as an empty magical circle.</font>

336
00:18:06,620 --> 00:18:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm...</font>

337
00:18:07,940 --> 00:18:13,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think that this is a bounded field
"world" that recreated reality.</font>

338
00:18:13,320 --> 00:18:16,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the slot machines and 
such aren't moving...</font>

339
00:18:16,460 --> 00:18:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's not continually reflecting
upon a real-life city...</font>

340
00:18:20,410 --> 00:18:24,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but copy-pasting the world periodically.</font>

341
00:18:25,270 --> 00:18:30,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps something that couldn't be copied
is right here in reality.</font>

342
00:18:32,770 --> 00:18:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone... is here.</font>

343
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are as always, Gil.</font>

344
00:18:40,140 --> 00:18:45,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You draw the destiny of the world
even after you have stopped functioning.</font>

345
00:18:49,860 --> 00:18:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's happening?</font>

346
00:18:51,400 --> 00:18:52,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I merely serve...</font>

347
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:55,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as a tool for someone.</font>

348
00:18:55,580 --> 00:19:00,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I were to put it in your words,
I guess I'd be a booster.</font>

349
00:19:00,380 --> 00:19:01,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

350
00:19:02,390 --> 00:19:03,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something wrong?</font>

351
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like we're in a subway train,</font>

352
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:09,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I've got three bars
on my cell reception.</font>

353
00:19:09,150 --> 00:19:10,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I might be able to do it right now.</font>

354
00:19:10,900 --> 00:19:12,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this an altar?</font>

355
00:19:12,840 --> 00:19:15,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A simple one at that.</font>

356
00:19:15,130 --> 00:19:19,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I can get the cell circuits
and the external forces to...</font>

357
00:19:20,660 --> 00:19:22,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got a connection!</font>

358
00:19:22,910 --> 00:19:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found you!</font>

359
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:32,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ayaka?</font>

360
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:35,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong? You're completely pale.</font>

361
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:39,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saber, you can't.</font>

362
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:40,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ayaka?</font>

363
00:19:40,370 --> 00:19:41,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't plan on</font>

364
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">saying or have the right to say
selfish things like, "Don't kill anyone."</font>

365
00:19:46,810 --> 00:19:48,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

366
00:19:48,290 --> 00:19:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you laugh at all times...</font>

367
00:19:51,460 --> 00:19:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and never abandon anyone!</font>

368
00:19:53,090 --> 00:19:55,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're different from me!</font>

369
00:19:55,690 --> 00:19:58,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if you ultimately soil those hands,</font>

370
00:19:58,170 --> 00:20:01,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the fact that you saved me
will not be erased!</font>

371
00:20:01,450 --> 00:20:02,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

372
00:20:03,280 --> 00:20:05,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I will do the dirty work"...</font>

373
00:20:05,770 --> 00:20:08,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is the one thing I don't want you to say.</font>

374
00:20:08,790 --> 00:20:12,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you need someone
doing the dirty work, I'll do it.</font>

375
00:20:14,540 --> 00:20:19,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to say that you worry
about the trivial things like always...</font>

376
00:20:19,820 --> 00:20:21,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but that's not the case.</font>

377
00:20:21,360 --> 00:20:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not.</font>

378
00:20:23,240 --> 00:20:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My encounter with you
isn't a trivial matter anymore.</font>

379
00:20:28,180 --> 00:20:31,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must risk my life to 
save that girl, then!</font>

380
00:20:31,670 --> 00:20:35,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In this world, we're 
starting off at the Church!</font>

381
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In place of the priest...</font>

382
00:20:37,110 --> 00:20:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we will protect her!</font>

383
00:20:40,030 --> 00:20:41,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Church...</font>

384
00:20:41,550 --> 00:20:42,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Protect...</font>

385
00:20:43,990 --> 00:20:45,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

386
00:20:45,510 --> 00:20:47,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">have met that golden guy—</font>

387
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:49,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ayaka?</font>

388
00:20:51,580 --> 00:20:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

389
00:20:52,770 --> 00:20:55,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were scouting the city streets
when that beast suddenly...</font>

390
00:20:56,120 --> 00:20:58,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beast? It can't be!</font>

391
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:04,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What...</font>

392
00:21:04,240 --> 00:21:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is that?</font>

393
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is everyone going to go 
somewhere else again?</font>

394
00:21:13,810 --> 00:21:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O girl...</font>

395
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">can you hear me?</font>

396
00:21:16,590 --> 00:21:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Black?</font>

397
00:21:18,820 --> 00:21:22,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, girl 
bewildered within a dream.</font>

398
00:21:22,130 --> 00:21:23,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you?</font>

399
00:21:23,220 --> 00:21:25,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Tsubaki Kuruoka.</font>

400
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:27,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

401
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:32,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am one that was once called
"a god of a particular place."</font>

402
00:21:32,940 --> 00:21:36,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nowadays, I'm merely that
which remains of said deity.</font>

403
00:21:38,170 --> 00:21:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But really, I'm so glad 
I got through to you!</i></font>

404
00:21:41,500 --> 00:21:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand your situation.
For the time being,</font>

405
00:21:44,370 --> 00:21:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine as long as you're all right.</font>

406
00:21:46,510 --> 00:21:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>One confirmation, though.</i></font>

407
00:21:48,330 --> 00:21:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did you see Ayaka Sajyou over there?</i></font>

408
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Ayaka is over here?</font>

409
00:21:53,540 --> 00:21:58,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sajyou has been witnessed in Snowfield
for the past few days.</font>

410
00:21:58,960 --> 00:22:01,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I contacted her myself.</font>

411
00:22:01,220 --> 00:22:02,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She is apparently...</font>

412
00:22:02,520 --> 00:22:04,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in Romania right now.</font>

413
00:22:05,280 --> 00:22:07,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If so, then...</font>

414
00:22:07,970 --> 00:22:09,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 11</font>

415
00:22:08,740 --> 00:22:09,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who is this girl?</font>

